1930;;Almost a Honeymoon;;British;;Monty Banks;;Clifford Mollison, Dodo Watts, Donald Calthrop;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Almost_a_Honeymoon_(1930_film);;An ambitious young man secures a job in the colonial service, the only stipulation being that he needs to be married which he isn't. He has just twenty four hours to find a woman to persuade to marry him.